UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.AllowPor: Determines if the Patchwork Tool can access any cable input or output ports on the device.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.EnabledO: Determines the game phases during which the device will be enabled. Pre-game includes all phases prior to start of game (like the pre-game lobby or countdown to start of game.) This setting does not affect Edit Mode.
Disables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.Enable.D: Enables the device when an event occurs.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.LegalInf: Please note: Use of a Patchwork audio device is limited to the creation of new and original musical works.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.Instrume: Selects which instrument sound will be applied to the audio output.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.AudioOut: Sets the destination for this device's Audio Out cable.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.DetuneIn: Sets the inputs for this device's Detune knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.Instrume: Sets the inputs for this device's Instrument carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.NoteIn.D: Sets the inputs for this device's Note In port.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.VibratoR: Sets the inputs for this device's Vibrato Rate carousel.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.VibratoI: Sets the inputs for this device's Vibrato knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.VolumeIn: Sets the inputs for this device's Volume knob.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.VibratoR: Sets the oscillation rate of Vibrato.
Sets the scale of an oscillating pitch offset of the audio output. This pitch fluctuation can add a wobbly characteristic to a sound.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.Detune.D: Sets the scale of the constant pitch offset of the audio output.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.Volume.D: Sets the volume of the audio output.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.CustomIn: Sets which custom fusion patch should be used, rather than the built-in instruments.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.OnDisabl: Triggers an event when the device is disabled.
UserOptionDefinition.Device_FabricInstrumentPlayer_C.OnEnable: Triggers an event when the device is enabled.
